    { title: '5 Signs You Should See an Internal Medicine Specialist', author: 'Dr. Anisha Natekar', date: 'April 2026', tag: 'Wellness', excerpt: 'Many chronic conditions are caught late. Recognise the early warning signs that warrant a specialist consultation.' },
  ];
